  "p06.sec.hours": { id: "Operating Hours Pattern", en: "Operating Hours Pattern" },
  "p06.hours.intro": { id: "Mayoritas outlet Fore Coffee beroperasi dengan jam standar, tapi ada variasi berdasarkan lokasi dan tipe outlet.", en: "Most Fore Coffee outlets operate with standard hours, but there are variations based on location and outlet type." },
  "p06.chart.hours": { id: "Distribusi Jam Operasional Outlet", en: "Outlet Operating Hours Distribution" },
  "p06.hours.insight": { id: "73% outlet beroperasi 07:00–22:00 (standar). Mall-based outlets (18%) mengikuti jam mall 10:00–22:00 — buka lebih siang, kehilangan morning rush. 24-hour outlets (3%) ada di area high-traffic seperti bandara dan stasiun. Extended hours (6%) beroperasi hingga 23:00–00:00.", en: "73% of outlets operate 07:00–22:00 (standard). Mall-based outlets (18%) follow mall hours 10:00–22:00 — open later, missing morning rush. 24-hour outlets (3%) are in high-traffic areas like airports and stations. Extended hours (6%) operate until 23:00–00:00." },
  "p06.sec.age": { id: "Store Age Analysis", en: "Store Age Analysis" },
  "p06.age.intro": { id: "Fore Coffee didirikan 2018 — pertumbuhan outlet menunjukkan fase ekspansi yang semakin agresif, terutama setelah IPO April 2025.", en: "Fore Coffee was founded in 2018 — outlet growth shows increasingly aggressive expansion phases, especially after the April 2025 IPO." },
  "p06.chart.age": { id: "Outlet Dibuka per Tahun (2018–2025)", en: "Outlets Opened per Year (2018–2025)" },
  "p06.age.insight": { id: "60+ outlet dibuka di H2 2025 (post-IPO) — akselerasi signifikan dibanding tahun-tahun sebelumnya. IPO fund (Rp 353B) langsung dieksekusi untuk ekspansi. Pertanyaan kritis: apakah outlet baru ini sudah breakeven, atau masih dalam fase ramp-up?", en: "60+ outlets opened in H2 2025 (post-IPO) — significant acceleration compared to previous years. IPO funds (Rp 353B) were immediately executed for expansion. Critical question: have these new outlets broken even, or are they still in ramp-up phase?" },
  "p06.callout.ipo.title": { id: "📈 Post-IPO Acceleration", en: "📈 Post-IPO Acceleration" },
  "p06.callout.ipo.text": { id: "Dari 2018–2024, rata-rata ~40 outlet baru per tahun. Di 2025 saja, 80+ outlet dibuka — doubling the pace. Ini sesuai dengan target IPO prospektus: 140 outlet baru + 30 Fore Donut. Execution speed menunjukkan pipeline lokasi sudah disiapkan sebelum IPO.", en: "From 2018–2024, average ~40 new outlets per year. In 2025 alone, 80+ outlets opened — doubling the pace. This aligns with IPO prospectus targets: 140 new outlets + 30 Fore Donuts. Execution speed shows location pipeline was prepared before IPO." },
  "p06.disclaimer": { id: "⚠️ Data outlet (350 lokasi, koordinat, tipe) berasal dari scraping API Fore Coffee yang real. Data transaksi bersifat sintetis. Proximity analysis menggunakan Haversine distance — jarak aktual jalan bisa berbeda. Angka distribusi regional dan operating hours adalah estimasi berdasarkan data yang tersedia.", en: "⚠️ Outlet data (350 locations, coordinates, types) comes from real Fore Coffee API scraping. Transaction data is synthetic. Proximity analysis uses Haversine distance — actual road distance may differ. Regional distribution and operating hours figures are estimates based on available data." },

