  "p07.callout.match.text": { id: "Dari data cleaning hingga executive summary, dari visualisasi hingga stakeholder communication — setiap aspek dari job description tercakup di portfolio ini. Bukan hanya teori, tapi implementasi konkret dengan data real (350 outlet dari API) dan analisis mendalam (16,229 transaksi bersih).", en: "From data cleaning to executive summary, from visualization to stakeholder communication — every aspect of the job description is covered in this portfolio. Not just theory, but concrete implementation with real data (350 outlets from API) and in-depth analysis (16,229 clean transactions)." },
